Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier 而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.20,0:00:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.47,0:00:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.11,0:00:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角  追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.58,0:00:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.52,0:00:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.13,0:00:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.10,0:00:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.77,0:00:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.27,0:00:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.61,0:00:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.21,0:00:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.25,0:01:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.88,0:01:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.39,0:01:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.72,0:01:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.36,0:01:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.99,0:01:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.73,0:01:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.50,0:01:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.33,0:01:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.13,0:01:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛從「半島」回國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.53,0:01:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿到不少關於久世的有趣情報喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.30,0:01:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長和少校被總理叫去了\N不在本部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.87,0:01:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我們先聽你的報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.97,0:02:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事啊？比這個案子更重要？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.48,0:02:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實是出現了難民集體武裝暴動的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.32,0:02:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.12,0:02:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,＃16  在那裏的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.49,0:02:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個別的11人引發自殺騷動以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.39,0:02:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面對急劇增加的反難民遊行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.03,0:02:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有報告說難民不斷地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.83,0:02:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從位於全國的居住區集結到長崎的出島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.70,0:02:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某些急躁的媒體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.57,0:02:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經開始鼓吹說那是難民集體武裝暴動的預兆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.54,0:02:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於這方面情況如何了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.71,0:02:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的確接到報告顯示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,檢舉非法脫離監視者的比率增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.99,0:02:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 要跟暴動連結在一起\N恐怕為時尚早吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.42,0:02:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們正在岸邊防止難民流入長崎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.66,0:02:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這樣說好像有點認知不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.83,0:02:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們海上保安廳這個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.30,0:03:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經阻止2艘可疑船隻\N16艘小艇接近出島海岸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.94,0:03:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民流入長崎已經是不言而喻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.61,0:03:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.04,0:03:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我們另外還有很多必須要處理的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.88,0:03:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是指個別主義者嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.75,0:03:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就想問公安部在做些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.08,0:03:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放任他們在本事件中煽風點火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.62,0:03:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罪過可是很重的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.16,0:03:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於那些自殺的個別的11人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.56,0:03:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要公安部事先掌握其所在\N根本是不合理的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.10,0:03:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在大部分的個別主義者\N雖然讚賞他們的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.74,0:03:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻也都作證跟他們劃清界線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.77,0:03:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.68,0:03:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於這次的難民問題\N我覺得防衛省也有責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對軍備擴張太過癡心妄想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.05,0:03:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然在他們面前搞實彈演習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.85,0:03:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果把睡著的人喚醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.42,0:03:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想爭論先有雞還是先有蛋的話\N在下樂意奉陪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.19,0:04:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這段時間吵著要管轄權的\N不正是那邊的警備部嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.26,0:04:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然你這麼說 那海自為什麼\N裝作一副沒看到的樣子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.23,0:04:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在提出管轄權問題之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.27,0:04:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你們能多協助我們這些挺身拚命的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.01,0:04:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 難民問題發展至此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.68,0:04:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們認為權限應該已經移轉給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.11,0:04:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還真敢說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.38,0:04:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回想一下前世紀的安保鬥爭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.85,0:04:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然這樣說對晚到的國防專業議員們很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.75,0:04:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我國的治安維持工作今後也將由警察來執行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.86,0:04:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然這些爭論也很重要\N不過 現在重點在各省廳間的共識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.97,0:04:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來您連心情愉快的空間都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.05,0:05:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我能力不足也是原因之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.42,0:05:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 大家僅止於爭取自身的特權\N將會看不見問題的本質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.66,0:05:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在明明是希望大家合力\N解決難民問題的時期啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.47,0:05:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您知道各國軍部和諜報機關\N逐漸弱化的最大理由嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.04,0:05:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛總理說的正是原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.51,0:05:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當站在組織頂端的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.55,0:05:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始利用組織當作自身爭權奪利的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,組織就開始緩慢死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.85,0:05:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 讓海上保安廳扮演吃虧角色\N我總覺得過意不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.16,0:05:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不一定哪時候也會碰到那種災難啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.43,0:05:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.90,0:05:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於難民的動靜\N有得到什麼具體的情報嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.81,0:05:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.87,0:05:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問總理知道什麼是中樞(Hub)電子腦嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.18,0:05:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.55,0:06:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校 請你說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.65,0:06:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總理 可以做有線通訊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.89,0:06:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.70,0:06:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,網絡原本沒有Hub也就是「中樞」這個概念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.21,0:06:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是最近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.37,0:06:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有台主機定義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.58,0:06:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,網絡上孤立意志的方向性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.01,0:06:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且借由邀請他們進入自己的電子腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.48,0:06:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出現了構築某種共同體的現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.85,0:06:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前那不過是以小規模宗教集團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.85,0:06:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或有魅力獨領風騷的藝人為中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.99,0:06:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有自治團體程度的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.69,0:06:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 在難民當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.16,0:06:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎出現了有能力籠絡他們\N讓他們滯留下來的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.40,0:06:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們認為那就是難民流入長崎的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.47,0:06:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可以說是一個…\N所謂指導者之類的存在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.64,0:07:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從常識來看很難想像是單獨一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然無法一概而論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.64,0:07:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 我不認為一個人的電子腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.08,0:07:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有能力跟300萬人的意志同時感應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.95,0:07:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 您若是問那是否\N像是指導者一般的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.65,0:07:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒可以說是那樣沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.49,0:07:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.86,0:07:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出現那樣的人物對政府而言是最大的威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請繼續保持警戒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.87,0:07:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想借由廢止難民特別處理法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,控制住難民特權的擴大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.61,0:07:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後從稅制問題著手解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.21,0:07:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是似乎有政敵巧妙地利用了這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要太過在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.79,0:07:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.99,0:07:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一件事要麻煩你們調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.66,0:07:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.43,0:07:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟日美安保條約有關聯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國防專業議員當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.20,0:08:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有人跟舊大日本技研有勾結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為本次安保的意義在於
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.64,0:08:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓世界上唯一擁有放射能除去技術的我國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.31,0:08:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠和依靠核武嚇阻力量的美帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.78,0:08:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有對等甚至更進一步的立場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.28,0:08:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不能達到這個目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.02,0:08:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次的安保延期簽訂也無妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.59,0:08:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.96,0:08:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—部分的議員和企業並不在乎這個理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.33,0:08:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這種事再重複下去\N這個國家過多久都不可能自立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個情報是哪裏來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.84,0:08:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從外務省的某個管道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.01,0:08:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們就馬上清查金錢的流向吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.14,0:08:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.14,0:08:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.01,0:08:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總理的個人利益和政治理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.48,0:08:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我應該認為您是\N基於哪一邊做的指示呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.15,0:08:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這還用說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.42,0:08:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.04,0:09:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我應該更早注意到才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.54,0:09:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茅葺總理正是課長喜歡的類型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.51,0:09:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 到現在才注意到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.89,0:09:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是敗給課長了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.76,0:09:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總理說的國防專業議員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.29,0:09:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是指高倉官房長官吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.73,0:09:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八成是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.26,0:09:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不認為他的目的只是賄賂地授受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.10,0:09:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,記得高倉不但親美而且是新保守派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.11,0:09:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還是拋棄不了美帝盲信主義的\N「軍工復合體」的最老資格者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.38,0:09:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對他來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.88,0:09:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大戰結束後失去商品價值的放射能除去技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.22,0:10:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要跟美帝聯手\N就可以變成對他國的新嚇阻力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.59,0:10:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且提高商品的價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.59,0:10:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他賄賂收賄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.76,0:10:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使軍備擴張成為泡影\N還是可以保住保守派的面子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.07,0:10:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這跟茅葺總理提倡的自立\N協調路線有很大的差異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.44,0:10:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他應該算是內廳的頭頭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上合田有在舊大日本技研
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.41,0:10:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,製作「日本的奇跡」的經歷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.58,0:10:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引誘難民發動恐怖攻擊以及日美安保條約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.39,0:10:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有核武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的復仇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.59,0:10:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有參與的價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.55,0:11:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等你好久了 茅葺總理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我馬上過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.67,0:11:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.47,0:11:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿東 有什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.07,0:11:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為召集名單沒有我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.97,0:11:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可以不參加吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.18,0:11:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個別主義者的秘密調查做得怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.91,0:11:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙比難民還沒有動靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.45,0:11:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們覺得好無聊喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.05,0:11:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼叫作好無聊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.89,0:11:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可是工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.29,0:11:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們還早得很呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.96,0:11:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候賭上歐亞霸權的\N無意義大戰好不容易才剛結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我那時候雖然多次潛入半島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.00,0:11:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在可是非常近代化了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.77,0:11:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經開始了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.34,0:12:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一邊等你一邊熱身當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.38,0:12:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多該開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.71,0:12:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才剛回國就讓您過度勞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.22,0:12:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.39,0:12:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.94,0:12:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,經過第4次大戰\N2024年時各國已經疲憊不堪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.44,0:12:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美帝趁大戰結束的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.38,0:12:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呼籲聯合國派兵到持續內戰的半島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.38,0:12:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然這也成為派遣自衛隊的直接契機…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.52,0:12:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實真相是美帝為了再度取回世界霸權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.22,0:12:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想把沉睡在北半島上的\N鈾礦開採權交給統一政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.66,0:12:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才把這件事當材料利用對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.43,0:12:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也是原因之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.87,0:13:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 那種想法雖然昭然若揭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.44,0:13:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但日本正熱烈製造戰爭特需物資
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.64,0:13:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能對聯合國說N0
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.44,0:13:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這對經歷2次大戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.18,0:13:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻除了根室奪回戰以外\N至今避免實戰的自衛隊來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.18,0:13:12.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根室：位於最接近北方四島的北海道最東端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這算是首次的試煉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.45,0:13:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 老大和少校他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.45,0:13:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是在戰時非公開地到海外去過嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.76,0:13:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.26,0:13:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時死於炸彈恐怖攻擊的首相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.29,0:13:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是少數有國際視野的政治家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.27,0:13:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也因為有這些內情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.30,0:13:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府為了打壓國內輿論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.04,0:13:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了嚴格的報導管制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.31,0:13:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還決定PKF的派遣地為比較安全的新義州
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.81,0:13:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到現在還記得當時的騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.95,0:13:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自衛隊進入當地後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.72,0:13:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所事事地跟居民們一起生活的報導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.05,0:13:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知不覺就沒人關心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.92,0:13:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多半會這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.42,0:13:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然實情並非如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.49,0:14:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至於負責執行報導管制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.10,0:14:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在幕後暗中活動的就是現在內廳的前身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.80,0:14:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內閣報導廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.00,0:14:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 PKF的真相是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.27,0:14:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比我以前聽說的狀況更加悲慘的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.18,0:14:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世所屬的部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.31,0:14:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是在本隊中也是最後進入當地的機動部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.88,0:14:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時新義州是特別行政府也是貿易據點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.82,0:14:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該在被攻擊的對象之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.53,0:14:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是統一政府成立後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.93,0:14:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敗退的人民軍殘黨所選擇的最後戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.30,0:14:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在新義州東方20公里左右的農村地帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.13,0:14:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,越過國境就是山嶽地帶嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.04,0:14:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者應該說是山頂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.01,0:14:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,標高充其量只有800米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.18,0:14:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 也算是個很適合打游擊戰的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.15,0:14:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到達之後不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.28,0:14:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,義體化步兵部隊就派出兩個中隊\N擔任游擊隊討伐隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.75,0:15:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始在極寒的山區移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.12,0:15:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然是第一次正式部署到戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.69,0:15:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 對PKF型號的混合式義體來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.46,0:15:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在零下20度的雪地行軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.83,0:15:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該也不會感到有太大壓力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.27,0:15:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時本隊收到情報顯示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.61,0:15:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人民軍最後的精銳部隊正企圖攻擊新義州
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.14,0:15:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此特別加強警戒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.11,0:15:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世的部隊正準備\N從北邊迂迴進入展開先制攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.12,0:15:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是先行的久世這一個小隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.59,0:15:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻在流經國境的河邊\N發現情報上沒提到的難民營
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.10,0:15:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏人民軍已經徒具名號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.87,0:15:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幾乎變成山賊的士兵們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.77,0:15:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在進行醜陋的搶劫行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.11,0:15:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世他們看到這個狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,義憤填膺地開始戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.55,0:16:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然是120對30的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.22,0:16:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻在一瞬間分出勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.89,0:16:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世待的這個小隊是義體化精銳部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.73,0:16:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是攻擊難民營的這群人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.86,0:16:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說原本是軍人\N卻大部分還是肉身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.40,0:16:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加上全部骨瘦如材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.11,0:16:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然後來收到好幾次人民軍的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然而實際的戰鬥卻只有這一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.99,0:16:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然極度寒冷以及不知道何時會打來的游擊隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.23,0:16:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使得大家被迫處於緊張氣氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.29,0:16:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是在市內駐紮的本隊\N狀態卻沒有那麼緊繃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.70,0:16:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還記得這個影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.57,0:16:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不久之後\N農村的小隊軍營就出現問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.94,0:17:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,PTSD嗎？（posttraumatic stress disorders）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.34,0:17:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.94,0:17:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「創傷後壓力癥候群」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.65,0:17:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次的戰鬥\N而且還是單方面殘殺對手的體驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.55,0:17:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢開始侵蝕年輕士兵的精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.59,0:17:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己的肺或臟器還沒換掉的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.43,0:17:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取得難民帶進來的合成酒精或大麻脂(hashish)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.43,0:17:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想盡辦法拚命逃避記憶中閃過的殺戮惡夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.47,0:17:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以往紀律良好的自衛隊\N一旦品行慢慢開始崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.41,0:17:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本的媒體就會開始無情的批評
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然難民營內殺戮的事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.38,0:17:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在報導管制下完全沒有洩漏給媒體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.82,0:17:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是正因為如此\N他們的態度受到強烈的批判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.93,0:17:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上下達了不讓媒體報導士兵醜態的規定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.53,0:17:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們的自由受到限制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.63,0:18:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情甚至演變到連回國都不准許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.40,0:18:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直就像隔離病房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.51,0:18:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪上加霜的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.54,0:18:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沿國境的難民營內的殘殺\N被一部分媒體得知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.95,0:18:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至有人開始散佈謠言中傷\N說那是不是日本自衛隊幹的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.49,0:18:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,農村的居民們激烈反應\N要求說明真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.39,0:18:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不要說在嚴格報導管制下的年輕士兵們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.06,0:18:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就連長官們也無法為自己辯護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.20,0:18:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能默默躲在帳棚裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.90,0:18:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的事情不斷繼續的某一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.31,0:18:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當地的記者對某個士兵說了這樣一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.51,0:18:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙恐怕是想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.98,0:18:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挖苦這個連自己的肺都沒有的士兵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.79,0:18:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.22,0:18:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道Assassin這個字的意思嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.96,0:19:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那在阿拉伯語的意思是「吸食大麻脂的人」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.37,0:19:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十一世紀時伊斯蘭的刺客會吸食大麻脂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.00,0:19:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後在夢遊狀態下暗殺\N奪回耶路撒冷的十字軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.64,0:19:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十字軍看到之後\N就很害怕地叫他們Assassin
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.72,0:19:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們也靠那玩意\N把這裏看成樂園嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.45,0:19:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把軍隊開進別人的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.15,0:19:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算當客人當到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.82,0:19:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這群殺人犯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干…幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.13,0:19:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.60,0:19:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們或許有當客人的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.94,0:19:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以跟你交換那個嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.28,0:19:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世這麼說之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.88,0:20:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就拿槍交換照相機進入難民營
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.69,0:20:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那他後來做了什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.33,0:20:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據說什麼都沒做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是拿著照相機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.73,0:20:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時透過取景器觀看難民的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.13,0:20:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時做做折紙而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.97,0:20:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.17,0:20:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也完全搞不清楚他真正的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.21,0:20:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不久後開始出現奇妙的現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.25,0:20:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先是老人們漸漸對久世感興趣\N到最後還請他喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.52,0:20:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來是小孩趁著叫他折紙飛機的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.22,0:20:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漸漸接近一句話都不說的久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.36,0:20:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後隔天連女人和成年男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.80,0:20:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都輪流想跟久世隨便聊聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.43,0:20:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世卻只是很高興地看著\N然後把這個狀況拍成照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.41,0:20:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.44,0:20:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.14,0:20:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,持續到三個月後人民軍投降\N自衛隊解除任務為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.58,0:21:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媒體後來就沒有人\N再提到殘殺的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.65,0:21:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後自衛隊歸國的前一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.45,0:21:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世突然從難民營失去蹤影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.12,0:21:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當地的難民營留有一張照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.53,0:21:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來的行蹤呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.43,0:21:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人說他越過國境向西走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.17,0:21:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過無法確定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.20,0:21:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他到底在哪裏 如何流浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.64,0:21:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,調查途中我跟一個自稱\N從台灣難民街回來的男子談過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.08,0:21:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說在那裏見過一個\N可能是久世的男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.38,0:21:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,義體的頭髮雖然完全變白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.65,0:21:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 他作證說那確實是久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.72,0:21:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了證明是久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.52,0:21:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說久世身邊總是有人\N很快樂地聚在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.96,0:21:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是日本人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.90,0:21:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.80,0:21:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 你會說話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.35,0:22:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 是少校啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.71,0:22:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已經回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.88,0:22:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 我一直在聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.05,0:22:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實很令人感興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.16,0:22:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.56,0:22:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然通過中樞電子腦的過濾陣列\N費了我不少功夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.73,0:22:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於能夠逆向搜尋\N難民的電子腦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.23,0:22:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是出島的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.64,0:22:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在請NSA幫忙確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.64,0:22:33.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,National Security Agency 美國國家安全局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.11,0:22:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該很快就能用影像確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.58,0:23:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我體內行星和星星的銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.25,0:23:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著它們每一個都唱著同樣寧靜的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.82,0:23:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在現實當中從來沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.79,0:23:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣美麗的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.16,0:23:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有一點懷疑或恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.67,0:23:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到一個聲音\N—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.81,0:23:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字\N—然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.37,0:23:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省視自身\N—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.41,0:23:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我\N—時間已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.68,0:23:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.99,0:23:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去讓這一切成真的\N—它就在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.06,0:24:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在軀殼裏的美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.33,0:24:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到一個聲音\N—醒來吧
